STRING.3: Armed with G36 Assault Rifles, Riflemen do the dirty work and are up to any task they're assigned.
Heavy Gunners are light armored infantry outfitted with 60-20 FN MAG machine guns. They relish close contact kills and make quick work of infantry and light vehicles.
Rocket Launchers carry MBT LAW Rocket Launchers ideal for turning vehicles into twisted, burnt out husks of scrap metal on the battlefield.
Flamethrowers love a good bonfire and burn through enemy infantry with M2-2 flamethrowers.
Nearly invisible to enemy units, Snipers pick off targets from a safe distance with their Savage 110 BA tactile sniper rifle.
Strapped with improvised explosives, Suicide Bombers' "ultimate sacrifice" brings ultimate destruction to all nearby units and buildings.
These grease monkeys don't let a little gunfire get in the way of vehicle repair.
Medics patch up your wounded on the battlefield.
Jackrabbits come with a big bite. These medium-armored, unmanned mini-tanks are mounted with M60E4 machine guns.
Fleet and aiming to kill, Rocket Buggies are light strike vehicles equipped with Hydra 70 rocket launchers.
Medium-armored jeeps with M2 heavy machine guns, Humvees fire .50 caliber rounds at 1,200 rounds/min.
Firing BGM-71 TOW missiles, Razorbacks are light-armored, mid-range strike vehicles that take aim at a safe distance.
Don't be fooled by these light tanks, Rhinos are medium armored with a 30 mm L21 cannon that punches holes in lighter vehicles.
Paladins are beasts on the battlefield. With 120 mm rifled main guns, these heavily armored medium tanks do serious damage.
Challengers are slow, but they're heavily armored and fire high explosive armor piercing rounds with a 128 mm main gun.
Laser Tanks are short range tanks with medium armor. Their high energy lasers burn hard and bright against all units.
AA Guns make it rain enemy aircraft -- these light weight vehicles are mounted with a powerful 8.8 cm Flak Cannon.
Jammer vehicles stun their targets with pulsed energy projectiles that create rapidly expanding plasma and no means of escape.
Interceptor tracks incoming missiles and shoots them out of the air.
Outfitted with a 280 mm C/34 main gun, Mega Tanks have no natural predators -- they are the heaviest, most powerful ground units available.
Wing Drones are lightning fast drones mounted with their Hydra 70 rocket pod.
Copter Drones are helio drones that sink their talons into targets from medium range with their L86 LSW machine guns.
Cobras are lightly armored helicopters mounted with twin MG 3 machine guns and the mobility to mow down infantry units.
UH-60s are heavy choppers humming with twin mounted AGM-114 Hellfire rocket pods.
Thunderbolts are light attack planes -- these birds of prey strike hard and fast.
Raptors bring the pain from above with strafing runs on ground units.
Hercules rules the battlefield in MK-8 armored exoskeletons outfitted with XM18 mini-guns and 25mm grenade launchers.
